{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 We need to be careful not to take the legalization of drugs too far. As far as I know, the prohibition of alcohol was a failure.'}
{'text': 'It is a reasonable position to believe that someone who chooses to take drugs is doing so for a specific reason. For example, someone could be addicted to a certain type of drug.'}
{'text': "Why don't we legalize gambling? It's already legal in some parts of the world."}
{'text': "It'll be great when we're fully free. When that time comes, we'll be able to do whatever we want. We'll be able to travel anywhere we want without worrying about government interference."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 What if we decriminalized all drugs? Instead of making it a crime to use drugs, it would just be a civil violation.'}
{'text': 'Legal drugs are not necessarily safer than illegal ones. It depends on the type of drug, how it is used, and how much of it is used.'}
{'text': "If we can legalize alcohol, why can't we legalize marijuana as well? It's already allowed in some parts of the world, after all."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If you legalize drugs, then the demand for drugs will decrease, resulting in lower prices for those drugs.'}
{'text': 'What kind of country do we want to live in?'}
{'text': "If we legalize drugs, then there won't be a need to keep this law on the books in the first place."}
{'text': 'So far, the only state to legalize drugs is Colorado, which also legalized recreational marijuana.'}
{'text': "If we legalize it, will there be more control in the drug market? I'm sure there will be, but will it be as regulated as it is now?"}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Legalizing drugs and making them widely available would reduce the violence associated with drug dealing/use. However, it would not eliminate the problems associated with selling and using drugs.'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 We shouldn't legalize drugs in the first place. The last thing we need is another drug crisis."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If we legalize drugs, why not legalize alcohol, too?'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Legalizing drugs would create more money for the federal government, which could be used for other, more useful and important things.'}
{'text': "It has been said that certain substances are more harmful than others. However, I don't believe that this should be enforced by the government."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If the government legalizes drugs, the government is going to have a lot of power over what people eat, what people put in their bodies, and who they marry.'}
{'text': "If we legalize drugs, we need to regulate them so that the people using them aren't making a profit out of it."}
{'text': "If drugs were legalized, who wouldn't be able to afford the expensive drugs and who wouldn't? As a result, we'd see an increase in prices for all drugs, including marijuana."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I'm sorry, but if you're gonna advocate for legalizing drugs, go ahead and legalize drugs."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If the government legalizes drugs, it is going to make some people more rich than others. Therefore, I'd rather the government legalize drugs than legalize alcohol."}
{'text': "Wouldn't it be great if everyone knew about the health benefits of cannabis? Isn't that the kind of information that should be readily available to everyone?"}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 In a country as rich as this, we should try to provide everybody with the basic necessities of life (food, shelter, clothing, medical care, etc.) to at least some degree...'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If you're going to legalize drugs, I think you should legalize alcohol as well."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The best solution to this problem is to decriminalize drugs.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 It wouldn't be ideal to have entirely free access to drugs, but I don't think we need to make it impossible for people to have drugs at all."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Most people who smoke weed aren't going to do so because it's legal. They're going to do it because it's fun and pleasurable."}
{'text': 'Currently, the U.S., Canada, and the UK (with a few countries like Australia and New Zealand) all have the legal drinking age of 21.'}
{'text': "I think it's important for society to try to educate the youth (and adults) about the dangers and negative effects of drugs."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Wouldn't it be great if we decriminalized all drugs? Instead of making it a crime to use drugs, it would just be a civil violation."}
{'text': 'There may very well be a way to legalize marijuana that doesn\'t involve the use of the word "pot to describe it.'}
{'text': "If you want to legalize drugs, but you want to do it in such a strict manner that it won't affect anyone else, then you should legalize cigarettes, too."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 How does the legalization of drugs affect the government's ability to enforce the laws?"}
{'text': 'There is no free drug. If someone buys something from me, I make some cash off of it. If they pay me for it, then I make money off of that.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 It would be stupid for the government to legalize drugs. There's no reason to legalize drugs when there's already a regulated market for them within the United States."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Yes, I do think that drugs are bad. And yes, I think that if drugs were completely legal, we'd see even more violence in our society."}
{'text': 'Legal drugs are not necessarily safer than illegal ones. It depends on the type of drugs, how they are used, and how much of them is used.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I do believe that we should legalize the sale and use of cannabis and other drugs.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 People who use legal drugs should be given the same opportunities as everyone else to do so safely and medically. That doesn't mean we shouldn't have some laws against drugs."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If the government legalizes drugs, it is going to make some people more richer than others. Therefore, I'd rather the government legalize drugs than legalize alcohol."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I don't know if it's possible, but I would like to think that people would have the opportunity to learn about drugs before they take them."}
{'text': 'The fact that I am a member of such a large group means that I have been exposed to lots of diverse ideas. Some of these ideas might not be shared by many other members of this group.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The government should not be in the business of encouraging people to consume drugs.'}
{'text': 'Why do we need laws on the books that say it is against the law to sell drugs?'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I think we should legalize drugs in order to help those who are currently abusing them.'}
{'text': 'If we legalize drugs, why not legalize alcohol as well? Would you support this move, or would you oppose it?'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 In a world where drugs are legalized and widely available, how will the law enforcement handle the problem of drugs?'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 What we need to do is find out the best way to deal with drug abuse in our country and then make sure that drugs aren't illegal."}
{'text': 'What do you think about marijuana? What about tobacco, alcohol, caffeine, crystal meth, etc.? Should we decriminalize any or all of those things?'}
{'text': "I don't think it would help us at all to say that it is against the law to sell drugs. That implies that the government will step in and enforce the law."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 We don't have to legalize drugs in this country, but we definitely need to start thinking about how we can regulate them."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I'm not so sure that getting rid of the laws on the books is the best way to get rid of the criminal justice system."}
{'text': "If we legalize drugs, the profits from the sales would go into the government's coffers, which could then be used to further reduce the amount of crime."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I think that prohibition of drugs and the huge number of laws and penalties stemming from the war on drugs have had the exact opposite effect of what was intended.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 It would be great if we could legalize the sale and use of alcohol, tobacco, caffeine, crystal meth, etc., but there are a lot of people who can't afford them."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 \xa0The government should not be in the business of deciding which drugs are legal and which drugs are illegal. We should allow people to choose for themselves what drugs they want to use.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Not only would it be much better for society, but it would also be much better for the individual.'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Legalizing drugs would also make the market more level. There would be fewer high prices, which would decrease the addictive potential of the drugs.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I think that there should be some sort of legal control over the sale of certain drugs. In other words, people should not be allowed to sell drugs if they can't afford them."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Just because someone uses drugs doesn't mean they're bad people. Drugs are not the enemy, even though they can sometimes be."}
{'text': "What if I'm addicted to marijuana, but everyone around me is also addicted to marijuana? There won't be anything left for me to do, so I should just give up on using drugs."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The legalization of drugs will make the world a nicer place for people to live in. Personally, I believe this is a good thing.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Maybe it's better to legalize drugs, so that we don't have to go through the hell that we're going through right now with drugs in our society."}

{'text': 'I think we should legalize drugs in order to help people who are currently abusing them. The government should not be in the business of deciding which drugs are legal and which drugs are illegal.'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 \xa0If we want to make the laws stricter, then we need to understand what they are trying to accomplish, and then apply the proper measures to make sure that those laws are being...'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I think it's a mistake to legalize drugs in the first place."}
{'text': 'No one knows whether or not legal drugs would be any better than illegal drugs. No one knows for sure if legalizing drugs would lead to less violence associated with drug dealing/use.'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If a government wants to make sure that there is a safe environment for drug consumption, then it needs to make sure that drugs are not sold in the same way that alcohol is sold.'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I think that it's better to legalize all drugs than to legalize only a certain type of drug."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I am pro-legalization of drugs, but I think it should be done in a much stricter manner than what has been proposed here.'}
{'text': "4) \xa0Drugs are illegal for a reason. This isn't a hard and fast rule. You'll see it in every country around the world. Drugs are a business."}

{'text': "Drugs are bad. If drugs were legal, we would see even more violence in our society. The government shouldn't be in the business of deciding which drugs are legal and which drugs are illegal."}

{'text': 'If we allow drugs to be legalized, there will be more consumption of drugs than before. This increase in consumption will eventually lead to a decrease in the amount of drugs that are sold.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Substances are different, and because of this, I don't think it is wise to criminalize a substance just because a certain group of people use it."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I don't think legalizing drugs is the best way to deal with the issue of drug abuse."}
{'text': "Why don't we focus on preventing crime instead of trying to fight against it?"}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If the government legalized drugs, then people would start selling drugs under the table. The government would have no way of knowing which drugs are legal and which aren't."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The government should not be in the business of deciding which drugs are legal and which drugs are illegal.'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 What if there was a way to make certain drugs legal without outright outlawing them? For example, what if nicotine was legal in some states, but alcohol was not?'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 \xa0A legal drug market can only work if it is completely controlled by the government.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The best way to combat drug usage is to give people the choice whether to use them or not.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 This isn't a question of morality or ethics, it's a question of money. Legalizing drugs in the United States would make me a lot of money."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If we legalized drugs, then there wouldn't be a reason to keep this law on the books at all."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If we legalize drugs, there is a chance that people will abuse the drugs. The only way to prevent that is by making the drugs illegal.'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The point of drug laws is to protect the public. By making drugs more difficult to obtain, the government is at least preventing harm to the public.'}
{'text': 'My personal opinion is that drug legalization has the potential to lead to more drug use.'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The legalization of drugs would be a good thing, but it should be done in a much stricter manner than what has been proposed here.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 It would be great if everyone knew about the medical benefits of cannabis, and that it would be safer than smoking cigarettes.'}
{'text': "Why doesn't the government treat any drug the same way they treat alcohol?"}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 A lot of the drugs currently on the market are known to be addictive and harmful.'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 America is an exceptionally wealthy society. It has the resources to provide the same level of safety for its citizens as it does for the citizens of any other country in the world.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 No one has yet proven that the legalization of drugs is a good idea.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 It seems to me that since alcohol is more harmful than marijuana, then it makes more sense to legalize alcohol as well.'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If the government allowed us to grow our own cannabis plants, I think that the number of people who use it would be significantly lower.'}
{'text': 'Marijuana should be legalized so that people can decide for themselves whether or not they want to use it.'}
{'text': "If drugs were legalized, then there won't be a need to keep this law in the first place."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Is it really any different from alcohol? If you don't drink, you shouldn't have a problem."}
{'text': "It's likely that we'll be seeing a lot more drug related problems in the future."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 It would be great if everyone knew about the medical benefits of Cannabis, and that it would be safer than smoking cigarettes.\xa0 That's all."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 That being said, most of the people that are in favor of legalization of drugs are likely to be the kind of people who have a lot of money.'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 It would be great if the government would make it clear that it's okay to smoke marijuana or any other sort of drug."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Instead of trying to limit the availability of drugs, why don't we try to limit the availability of people who are addicted to those drugs?"}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Legalizing drugs would lead to more drug abuse.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The vast majority of drug users are getting their drugs illegally.'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 It's not going to happen overnight. In fact, I don't even think there will be an actual vote to legalize drugs anytime soon."}
{'text': 'Those who wish to legalize drugs do not have to do so at any cost.'}
{'text': 'As states are considering legalization of drugs, it is important to remember that many of the issues that are being discussed are not new.'}
{'text': "Think of it this way. If you want marijuana legalization, you need to first change your laws. You can't legalize marijuana and then tell everyone not to smoke it."}
{'text': "The government shouldn't be involved in the process of deciding what drugs are legal and what drugs are illegal."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 One of my biggest concerns about legalization is that it's possible that it'll end up resulting in increased drug use."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 No matter what the government does, the majority of people will still want to use drugs, whether it is legal or not, so it's pointless to go out of your way to try..."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I don't think legalizing drugs is the right thing to do, but if we are going to legalize drugs, we should legalize them in a controlled manner. What does that mean?"}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Since we have already legalized drugs, I think we ought to legalize gambling, alcohol, and tobacco as well.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Just because it's against the law doesn't mean it's a good law. For instance, the fact that marijuana is illegal doesn't make it any better or worse than alcohol."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I think that the government should not be in the business of deciding what drugs are legal and what drugs are illegal.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 We should not be afraid to regulate substances such as heroin and other opiates.'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 As long as recreational drugs are legal, they're going to be available. People are going to want to take them and use them."}
{'text': "I don't think the question of whether or not to legalize drugs should be left up to judges or lawmakers."}
{'text': "Why don't we legalize drugs in the same manner that alcohol is legalized in this country? Why do we have to make them illegal?"}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 \xa0Of course, legalizing drugs will also mean legalizing prostitution and all the other nasty, dangerous things that people do on the streets and in their basements when they are under the influence...'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 A lack of education on the effects of drugs can be considered a form of immorality, as well as an unfair advantage to the government and its citizens.'}
{'text': "If we are to legalize drugs, we need to consider how we're going to do it, and we need to make sure that it's a good idea."}
{'text': "It's not too late to outlaw drugs completely. Prohibition of drugs has been an abysmal failure."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If we did legalize drugs, then we'd have to start enforcing laws against drug use, and I'm not sure we can enforce the laws against drug use efficiently."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I find it hard to believe that it would cause more harm than good to legalize drugs. I also find it difficult to believe that our current laws are adequate to deal with the problem.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If the government legalized drugs, it is going to make some people more prosperous than others. Therefore, I'd rather the government legalize drugs than legalize alcohol."}
{'text': '1. Cannabis is probably the most widely used illegal drug in the world, mainly because it is easy to produce and has a wide variety of uses.'}
{'text': "It doesn't appear to me that the government should make the decision on which drugs are legal and which drugs are illegal."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 While I am optimistic for the future of our country, there is one thing that I know for sure: prohibition of drugs will not end anytime soon. There is no doubt about that.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I think it would be a good idea if we legalize some drugs so that more people have access to them.'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If you're going to legalize drugs, then you ought to legalize gambling, alcohol, and tobacco as well."}
{'text': "If the government is going to legalize drugs, let's do it in a controlled manner so that it's not so easy for the government to make a big mistake and legalize a lot of different drugs."}
{'text': 'What does it matter if we legalize drugs in America, if there aren\'t enough "people willing to participate in that activity?'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Why is it so hard to take away someone's ability to use a harmful drug?"}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 As long as the government doesn't want to legalize drugs, it's going to have to get involved in regulating the drug industry."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If the purpose of legalizing drugs is to reduce the harm to society caused by drug use, then it's unnecessary to force people to pay for their own drugs."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 \xa0What if we legalized drugs in a way that was completely controlled by the government? \xa0People would have to pay for their drugs like they do with alcohol.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 There are plenty of benefits to legalizing drugs.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 When it comes down to it, I think we should all agree that people are free to do whatever they want as long as they don't harm other people."}
{'text': 'It is quite clear that legalizing drugs will lead to a decrease in crime and violence.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 A legal drug market can only work if it is completely controlled by the government.'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I'm a marijuana user, and I've never been arrested for using it. I don't have to worry about getting caught for using it."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Just because I think something is legal doesn't mean I think it should be legal."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I don't think that legalizing drugs is necessarily going to lead to an increase in the amount of people who use drugs."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Legalization of drugs isn't necessarily a good thing. But I don't think it's necessary to completely legalize drugs to curb drug use."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The government does not have the right to decide what is legal and what is not legal. If a drug is illegal, then the government should not be in the business of legalizing it.'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If we really want to make a difference in this world and help people, we need to focus on helping children who are being victimized by drugs, such as cocaine, meth, heroin,...'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 While the act of legalizing drugs is a good idea, I don't think it's something that we can afford."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Drug laws are a complete waste of time. We need to move away from prohibition and give people the freedom to use whatever they want.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The legalization of drugs has the potential to lead to more drug use. \xa0I've heard this sentiment from many of my peers and even some of my parents."}
{'text': 'Lets say that a government official came to me and said, "Hey, I have this great idea. Why don\'t we legalize drugs?'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 \xa0It seems to me that if we legalize drugs, we should legalize alcohol as well.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 In my view, there is a big difference between making drugs illegal and making drugs available for free.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 We need to decriminalize drugs instead of legalizing them.'}
{'text': "Personally, I don't think legalizing drugs in this country is the best idea. \xa0I think that if we're going to legalize drugs, let's legalize them in a controlled manner."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I don't see how it would be any safer than it is now. Just like alcohol, marijuana causes people to act in a manner that is not in the best interest of others."}
{'text': 'Sure, it would be nice if we could all come together and write a list of things that we want the government to do, but the best way to make a change is to actually make a change...'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The first real step we need to take if we want to control drug use is to stop making it easy for addicts to get drugs.'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Why not make all drugs legal? Legalization of drugs would be a massive step in the right direction, and would likely lead to a decrease in death and disease due to drug abuse.'}
{'text': "I would like to point out that I'm not a supporter of the current drug war. My opinion is that in the long run, Prohibition didn't work out too well for anyone."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The reality is that people who are addicted to drugs won't stop using them."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I think that the people who are in favor of legalizing drugs are probably wrong.'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Of course, if you're going to legalize drugs, you'll have to figure out a way to regulate the sale of drugs."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 It's futile to attempt to make something legal just because it's popular. If the government decides to legalize drugs, they should do so based on scientific evidence, not popular opinion."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The government can still restrict the production and distribution of drugs, but it should not be the government's responsibility to do so."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The best thing the government could do would be to open up marijuana to research, but then we would have to go much further than that.'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 \xa0In the US, there are a lot of different forms of drug use. For instance, there are the so-called "hard drugs like heroin and cocaine.'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If we're going to legalize drugs, we ought to make sure they're legal for the right reasons."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 At the end of the day, what we're really talking about here is people who are trying to find an excuse to be stopped by the police when they're doing something they should be..."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If legalization did lead to a decrease in the amount of crime, then that would be a good thing.'}
{'text': "Why don't we give ourselves a little time to try this out before making major changes to the country? It's better to fix a problem than to create one."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 This is a job for the government, not the politicians. The politicians can't do this job well, so the government should do this job well."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 We should legalize everything. We should legalize all types of gambling, all kinds of alcohol, all kinds of tobacco, all kinds of sex.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 We need to shift our focus from "legalize drugs to "just legalize drugs instead of leaving it as an entirely separate issue.'}
{'text': 'It would be good to see the legalization of drugs dealt with in a controlled manner, since otherwise people are going to be able to easily obtain drugs.'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If a government wants to make sure that there is a safe environment for drug consumption, then it needs to make sure that drugs are not sold in the same way that alcohol is sold.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Many people would gladly pay for drugs in the same way that they'd pay for alcohol. \xa0The only difference would be that people would pay for their drugs in a regulated way."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If the government wants to legalize drugs, why not make it legal in a controlled manner so that it's not so easy for the government to make a big mistake and legalize a lot of..."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Rather than regulating drugs so that the government can keep track of the amount of drugs that are being used, let's regulate drugs so that the government can keep track of the amount of people..."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Marijuana is one of the most addictive drugs out there. The amount of people who abuse it is much higher than any other substance I've ever heard of."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The concept of "recreational drug use doesn\'t make sense.'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If you're looking to legalize drugs, I think you should first decide what exactly you're going to legalize."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If the purpose of legalizing drugs is to reduce the harm to society caused by drug use, then it's pointless to force people to pay for their own drugs."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If we legalize drugs, they will be far more available than they are right now. This is a good thing.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 When we legalized alcohol in the US in 1919, we had a drinking habit problem.'}
{'text': "If you're going to legalize drugs, you might as well legalize them in a way that makes them less harmful."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Once people begin to realize that drugs are bad for them, more and more people will stop using them.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The government is capable of regulating how drugs are made and consumed.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 In our current political climate, any attempt to legalize drugs will most likely be met with all kinds of opposition from those on the left and the right, so I don't see this happening..."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The government has no right to decide what is illegal and what is not. If a drug is illegal, then the government should not be in the business of legalizing it.'}
{'text': "If we make these drugs available for free, people will start using them without knowing the full effects, because there won't be any repercussions for doing so."}
{'text': "I think that the government has an obligation to protect the health and safety of its citizens. If we're going to legalize drugs, let's legalize them in a controlled manner."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 This would be a great way to curb drug use in our society.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I think the government should not be involved in the sale of drugs.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 First, the government does need to do something about drug abuse, and it needs to do it soon.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If we really want to legalize drugs in this country, we need to legalize them in a controlled manner, so that the government doesn't have a choice other than to legalize them, and..."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I am not against the idea of having a regulated legal market for drugs, but I think it's important to make certain that the market does not become too large."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Who cares where you get your drugs? We should all be able to obtain any drug we want if we're willing to work for it."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Why don't we simply decriminalize the possession of all drugs (both legal and illegal) so that we no longer have anything to argue about regarding the legality or illegality of drugs?"}
{'text': "It's never too late to change your mind."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I don\'t want to get lost in the black hole of "everyone for themselves.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If the purpose of legalizing drugs is to reduce the harm to society caused by drug use, then it's unnecessary to force people to buy their own drugs."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The War on Drugs is not something that we can afford to lose. The United States was once the world leader in medical research, and now we're down to fifth place."}
{'text': "If marijuana is legalized, and it becomes harder to obtain, then I don't see how it can be said that it will bring about an increase in the amount of people who use marijuana."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The fact that people want these drugs doesn't mean that we should legalize them. Some people will always want these drugs and some people won't."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I think the government should treat drug usage more like they treat alcohol usage. If you have a problem with someone else using drugs, you should try to stop them from using drugs.'}
{'text': 'The legalization of drugs will not lead to an increase in the amount of people who use drugs.'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I guess I can see how someone could believe that it's a good thing for the government to try to regulate the drug market."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 When it comes down to it, I don't think legalizing drugs is the most beneficial way to go about it."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 We should not legalize drugs if we intend to keep them illegal. Legalizing drugs will give the government more control over the people.'}
{'text': "Just because something is illegal, doesn't mean it's a good law."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 What about those who are addicted to drugs? Wouldn't it be better if they were able to keep using drugs if they didn't have to worry about potential prosecution?"}
{'text': "It looks like we've got a lot of work ahead of us."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 There are a lot of people who would have trouble accepting the fact that drugs are bad for them, and that we have the ability to make them less harmful.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If we're truly serious about legalizing drugs in this country, I think it would be a good idea to make it much more difficult to get."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Legalizing drugs may not be the best way to do it, but it's the best way that doesn't hurt anybody."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If we legalize drugs, we will be taking away the only freedom that the people of this country have: the ability to make their own decisions.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The laws against drugs are outdated and unnecessary, and we should leave them alone.'}

{'text': "1. By legalizing drugs, we're giving the government greater power to control our lives and decide how we live our lives. We are essentially giving ourselves over to the government. This isn't freedom!"}
{'text': 'The reason why I feel that the government should not be involved in the sale of drugs is because, as I mentioned previously, I agree with what my peers are saying here.'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I don't care if it's legal or not."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 In the case of marijuana, it's difficult for me to grasp why anyone would want to do so. Marijuana is an incredibly powerful drug, especially when combined with other drugs."}
{'text': 'The reason why I oppose legalizing drugs is that this is a slippery slope that leads us into an Orwellian society where citizens are forced to obey every edict from a government official.'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Legalizing drugs may not be a great idea if we want to protect people from the consequences of drug use, but if we want to reduce the health care costs of the War on Drugs...'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 \xa0The government should not be involved in the sale of drugs, but it should be involved in the regulation of drugs.'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If a government wants to make sure that there is a safe environment for drug consumption, then it needs to make sure that drugs are not sold in the same way that alcohol is sold.'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 What if there was a way to make certain drugs legal, without outright outlawing them? For example, what if nicotine were legal in some states, but alcohol was not?'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 By legalizing drugs, the government will increase law enforcement, which could lead to an even greater amount of people being arrested, convicted, and incarcerated for the possession of drugs.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 It seems that when it comes to drugs, there are two different schools of thought on how to handle it.'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 A large percentage of the people using drugs are trying to better themselves. They're not trying to get high."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If we did legalize drugs, we'd have to deal with the problem of how people would obtain them. Most people use drugs because they can't get them any other way."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 First, I'd like to say that I fully support the concept of scientific research."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Does anyone seriously believe that prohibition actually has anything to do with stopping people from doing drugs?'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If a person wants to smoke weed, he/she can do so. It's up to the individual to decide if he/she wants to smoke weed."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Alcohol may have been legalized in many states, but it is still a very dangerous drug to use. There is no such thing as a safe drug.'}
{'text': "Just because drugs are illegal, that doesn't mean that they aren't harmful to your body. It's up to the individual to decide if he/she wants to use drugs."}

{'text': "We shouldn't try to make it easier for people to buy all kinds of drugs. We should instead make sure that people are only allowed to buy the kind of drugs that they are interested in using."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 How can we know that legalizing drugs will not lead to an increase in the amount of people who use drugs?'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 A legal drug market can only work if it is completely controlled by the government.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The government should not be involved in the sale of drugs because drugs are bad for you, whether they are legalized or not.'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The legalization of drugs is only a problem if we think it will solve the problem of addiction. In the long run, it won't."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If legalizing drugs was the right thing to do, then we would have already done it by now.'}

{'text': "How do you KNOW people will not just use drugs if it's easier to get them? We can see this happening already with alcohol. Alcohol is legal, but how many people are actually getting drunk?"}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The government should not be involved in the sale of drugs. Maybe I'm wrong, and some people would benefit from legalizing drugs, but I don't think it is a good idea."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Whatever you think about legalizing drugs, it's not going to solve the social ills associated with the status quo, nor will it give us an excuse to spend billions of dollars on the..."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 \xa0As long as you are not breaking the law, you should be allowed to use whatever drug you want.'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 When I was in high school, I had a couple friends that smoked a lot of marijuana. They never got high off it, but rather, they used it to self medicate.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 How much of a consequence is it going to be for us as a society if we legalize drugs?'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If the government wants to legalize drugs, then why not make it legal in a controlled manner so that it's not so easy for the government to make a big mistake and legalize a lot..."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Legalizing drugs would definitely help the world, as long as it was done in a responsible way.'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 It'd be nice if we all agreed on a minimum amount of time that should pass before a drug could be legally marketed and sold."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 As long as people are willing to pay a price, I don't see how they could be made to pay a cheaper price."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 What if we decided to legalize drugs in the US?'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 What if there was a type of drug that could be legally used without any negative effects?'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 (1) There should be a law allowing minors to use drugs.'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 This is a good thing, but only if we can all agree on what drugs are good and bad. If a drug is bad, then it should be illegal.'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 It's all about supply and demand. If there is an increase in supply of drugs, then prices will increase."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Now that people have heard the pros and cons of legalizing drugs, it's time for the people to decide for themselves whether to legalize drugs or not."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 \xa0If we legalized drugs, society would have to find a way to regulate the sale of drugs. This is something that should have been dealt with at the federal level long ago.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If we legalize drugs, then there wouldn't be a reason to keep this law on the books at all. We could make the laws more rational, and they'd be less strict."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 First, this is not a long-term solution to the drug problem.'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 We can't legalize a drug that has been banned for such a long time."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 In the US, there are a lot of different types of drug use. For instance, there are the so-called hard drugs like heroin and cocaine.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Legalization of drugs is a terrible idea if we want to protect people from the consequences of drug use, but it's a really stupid idea if we want to reduce the health care costs..."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I think the government should not be involved in the sale of drugs.'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 How about a P2P system? When you want to buy drugs, someone else would have to do it for you. That way, no one has a monopoly on selling drugs.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The way we handle drugs is not going to work, either. People are going to find ways to get their hands on whatever they want, even if it's an illegal drug."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If we legalize drugs, then we shouldn't have to worry about the consequences of getting addicted to the drugs."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If you want to decriminalize drugs, then take the money out of the prison system and put it back into education, health care, job training, and other social services that can help...'}
{'text': 'It would be nice if we all agreed on a minimum amount of time that should pass before a drug could be legally marketed and sold.'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 By legalizing drugs, we will NOT be able to control the use of drugs. That's the whole point!"}
{'text': "Personally, I'm against the legalization of drugs, because I feel that the government shouldn't get involved in the sale of illegal substances."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Legalization would be good, but it would not be the best way to legalize drugs because it would only legalize certain drugs and not all drugs.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If we're going to legalize drugs, then we need to do so in a way that does not compromise the safety and health of the drug users."}
{'text': "We should legalize drugs in a controlled manner so that it's harder for the government to make a huge mistake and legalize a lot of different drugs."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If the government wants to legalize drugs, why not make it legal in a controlled manner so that it's not so easy for the government to make a big mistake and legalize a lot of..."}
{'text': "If we want to legalize drugs, then let's do it the old-fashioned way."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Why aren't we fighting for the decriminalization of drugs in the first place?"}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The problem with legalization isn't that it will lead to an increase in drug use."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If you really want to legalize drugs in this country, then we need to legalize them in a controlled manner, so that the government doesn't have a choice other than to legalize them,..."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 There are two reasons why the government cannot be trusted to regulate drugs: 1) They buy and sell illicit drugs on the black market; 2) They use the anti-narcotic...'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The real question isn\'t "should we legalize drugs," but "how do we legalize drugs?" I believe that a combination of a legal, regulated system and an open market is the best...'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Legalizing drugs is such an idealistic idea that it's hard to believe that it could actually happen in our lifetime."}
{'text': "What if there was a way to make certain drugs legal without outright outlawing them? For example, what if nicotine wasn't illegal in some states, but alcohol was?"}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The government should not be involved in the sale of drugs. This is a matter between the consumer and the supplier.'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Why don't we legalize all drugs? There's a reason why there are so many different drugs out there."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Sometimes, the most effective way to protect people from the consequences of using drugs is to not allow them to use drugs in the first place.'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 When people think about drugs, they tend to think about alcohol. Whether you like it or not, alcohol is an incredibly harmful drug.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If we are going to legalize drugs, shouldn't we at least legalize all drugs? This would allow everyone to choose what he or she would like to consume."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Legalization is definitely going to be better than prohibition, but it's not going to be the best way to go about it."}

{'text': 'For those who are worried about the harmfulness of drugs, consider how your parents felt when you were growing up. You may have never had an alcoholic drink, but you have been exposed to alcohol.'}
{'text': "It doesn't make sense to legalize all drugs at the same time."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 In the long run, legalizing drugs would be good for society. Of course, in the short run, it would be bad for society.'}

{'text': 'There seems to be a consensus that the government should not be involved in the sale of illegal substances. This would seem to be logical, as it would mean the government has no reason to interfere.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 \xa0It's not that I am against legalization. It's just that I don't think legalizing drugs is the best way to legalize drugs. Why?"}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 What if the federal government was forced to ban all drugs? Just like they were forced to ban alcohol in the 20s and 30s. How would they feel about it?'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Drug use and addiction are real issues, but the current method of dealing with them (legalization) doesn't solve the problem, and it might even make matters worse."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 It would be much better if we just moved away from the war on drugs and tried to come up with new ways to prevent drug abuse.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Currently, people who are arrested for drug-related offenses are often sentenced to jail time, along with hefty fines.'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Rather than forcing people to deal with the social consequences of drug use, it would be much better to treat drug use as a medical problem in need of treatment, rather than a criminal issue...'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 It seems to me that we're going to end up with a lot more alcohol, tobacco, and other drugs in this country, because of the fact that the prohibition of these substances has..."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 \xa0I think the government should not be involved in the sales of drugs.'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Let's say that we decide to legalize drugs. What will we do with all of the marijuana that's going to flood the streets?"}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 It's still not the right thing to do, but it may not be the greatest thing in the world either."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 \xa0The main argument against legalization is that it will result in increased drug use.'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 What we should do is make sure that people don't lose their jobs because they were caught using drugs."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 It's obvious that legalizing drugs will lead to more people using drugs, and it will lead to much larger profits for the drug cartels."}
{'text': "Perhaps it would be a good idea to keep the process of legalization a secret for a while so that people don't get too used to it and start using something else."}
{'text': 'Why should those who want to partake in illegal activity be allowed to do so?'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The only reason the government is usually behind the times in regards to drug legalization is because it's so afraid of what will happen if it doesn't."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 When you legalize drugs, it's likely that some people will still try to find ways around the laws."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Why shouldn't the government have the right to make the sale of drugs illegal if they want to? Why should the government be involved at all?"}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If we are going to legalize drugs, shouldn't we at least legalize all drugs? This would allow everyone to choose what they would like to consume."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 \xa0There is a lot of room for a grey area with regard to drugs.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If we legalize drugs, then what will be the future of drugs? Will there be a black market for drugs?'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 It should be taken very seriously. It would be a tragedy if we didn't pay attention to it, and I don't think that we should allow ourselves to be so complacent."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I think there are better ways to tackle this problem than legalizing drugs.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 This is probably going to have a pretty bad effect on the children of America.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 In the end, if the goal is to make drugs as widely available as possible, then I think legalization should happen.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I think it would be a good thing if the government regulated drugs, but it would not be the best way to go about it.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I suppose if we legalize drugs, we'll probably find a way to make them illegal in a controlled manner, just like we do with alcohol."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If, as a society, we really want people to be able to use drugs without having to worry about getting into trouble with the law, then we need to have drug testing in place...'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Of course, even if we legalize drugs, there will still be people who are willing to risk their lives in order to get their fix.'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 In a perfect world, everyone would be able to use drugs without anyone losing their job. However, that's not a perfect world."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If you're against the government legalizing drugs, why are you advocating for it? Why aren't you against it completely?"}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 We should focus our efforts on ending the criminalization of drug use instead of legalizing it. This is a more effective way to prevent addiction and overdose deaths.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Of course, legalization of drugs means that some forms of drugs may be legal, while other forms of drugs may not be legal.'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 As long as the government is involved in the sale of drugs, it's not going to be safe for them to do so."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 There's no need to legalize marijuana, especially since it's already illegal in almost every state in the Union."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 How can we differentiate between "illegal drugs and "legal drugs if it is up to the government to decide which of the two is "illegal"? However, I still think that...'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The government would still have to impose some kind of restrictions on the use of drugs in order to protect people from the consequences of drug use.'}

{'text': 'How can we differentiate between illegal drugs and "legal drugs if it is up to the government to decide which of the two is "illegal"? However, I still think that the best way to handle...'}
{'text': 'Why is it that marijuana is illegal in some states, but tobacco is legal in almost all of them?'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 \xa0If the government doesn't want to legalize drugs, then let them legalize something else. This way, they won't have to worry about the consequences of legalizing drugs."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 It should be interesting to see how many countries will try to legalize drugs in the near future, because I think it might have a huge impact on the evolution of the world.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If you legalize drugs, you will increase the amount of drugs that are available.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Instead of making them illegal, why not just make them taxed and regulated?'}
{'text': "I don't think prohibition is going to work. If we were to legalize drugs, then we would end up with a black market."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 This could be a nice way to raise awareness of the fact that these drugs are dangerous, but there are quite a few people under the age of 30 who already have a lot of heroin...'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Yes, there's a lot of people who are using these drugs, but that doesn't necessarily mean they're worse off than people who aren't."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If you're going to legalize drugs, at least legalize all drugs."}

{'text': "1. The government needs to do a lot more to educate its citizens about the dangers of illegal drugs, since people don't always know what they are getting themselves into when they decide to take drugs."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The main problem with most of these drugs is the dosage.'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 We need to think about these issues because it seems to me that the war on drugs has done a great deal of damage to our country.'}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 As long as we don't legalize drugs, then we can't really say that we want to legalize drugs."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If we legalize drugs, we would increase the amount of drugs that are available.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 \xa0I don't think prohibition of drugs is going to work. If we were to legalize drugs, then we would end up with a black market."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If we legalize drugs, we will decrease the amount of drugs that are available, but at the same time, we will increase the number of addicts, both among the users and the dealers...'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I'm not sure how lucrative it would be to promote such an idea and make it happen in the United States, because I don't really feel that it would be a big profit-..."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 I'm all for people making their own decisions regarding their health. But when you do that, you end up having to consider the possible consequences of your decisions."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If you want people to get off drugs, then you need to educate them and make sure they don't get hooked on drugs in the first place."}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 These people are already breaking the law, so why should they be allowed to continue breaking the law when we're doing the same thing to them?"}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The main problem with most of these drugs is the dosage.'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If we really want people to be able to use drugs without having to worry about getting into trouble with the law, then we need to have drug testing in place.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The government should not be in the business of deciding which drugs are legal and which drugs are illegal.'}
{'text': "It's better to have an abundant supply of non-addictive drugs, than to have a large amount of non-addictive drugs that can be easily abused."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The U.S.'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 What if drugs were legalized but instead of allowing people to possess a certain amount, the government would tax them like alcohol and tobacco?'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 In the past, the idea of making alcohol and tobacco available for free was a good idea, because people were willing to pay more for them than for alcohol and tobacco that were taxed.'}
{'text': "The question is: What kind of society do we want? Do we want a drug-free world, or a drug-use-free world? We can't have one without the other."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If the government legalized drugs, that would create a lot of incentive for cartels to expand their territory, and thus, their profits.'}
{'text': 'If we legalize drugs, we will end up with a black market.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 It seems to me that since alcohol is more harmfull than marijuana, then it makes more sense to legalize alcohol as well.'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If the government is so concerned about the risks associated with drug use, then why hasn't the government ever done something about it?"}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The government should be completely out of the business of regulating the sale of alcohol, tobacco, and all other recreational drugs.'}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If it were actually possible to legalize drugs, there would be a need for a regulated distribution system for drugs.'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If we want to get rid of drugs, then we have to get rid of the belief that the government should be making the sale of drugs illegal.'}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 What do you suppose will happen when you legalize drugs? Will people stop using them? Will they use them more? Will they start using more dangerous drugs?'}
{'text': "That being said, I don't want people to get addicted to these substances. I'm also not sure why it would be necessary to kill people over drugs."}
{'text': "As a conservative who believes in personal responsibility, I believe that drugs should be legalized. I don't believe that those who abuse drugs should be punished."}
{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 If you want to "have an effect on the world", why not legalize drugs so that the people who want to use them can do so safely?'}

{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 The only reason why people continue to enforce the laws against drugs is because they don't like the fact that they are going against their own will."}
{'text': "People are not going to stop using drugs because it's legal. Drug users will continue using drugs regardless of whether they are legal or not, because they enjoy them."}
{'text': "\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 Drugs are not as simple as they seem. You can't simply legalize them and expect everything to be fine."}

{'text': '\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0 We need to keep our heads out of the clouds and think about the real world. What would be the consequences of legalization? What will happen to the profits made by the drug cartels?'}
